scenes.title: Soul Magic Arcania
scenes.description: Arcania is the magic fantasy world of Soul Magic, where you can collect resources, train skills, craft wearables and trade items! Collect ores and magic stones from mining, farm plants, alcehmize for alloys and craft wearables, fish and cook! You can also trade resources for Gold Midas, the currency of Soul Magic. Soul can be recovered from meditation at Elswyth Magic School in Land (-95, -89). We are also running the Admission Carnival. Players who pass the admission quiz will be awarded the Sunstaff, a magic staff that gives you spell casting ability!

scenes.title: Fuego Fortress
scenes.description: Fuego Fortress is Nikki Fuego's 2023 Game Jam submission. In this scene Nikki used AI for every single texture, skybox, NPC dialogue, NPC style concepts, and maze layout on each floor. This entire scene was made in SDK7 with the Visual Studio SDK7 Editor Extension. This is an 8x8 estate. The entirity of this scene was made during the Game Jam duration; nothing here was reused from previous projects. In this lucid dream you journey through the Fortress to discover your true identity and purpose in this universe.

scenes.title: Wirtualna PKO Rotunda
scenes.description:
On May 30, 2023, the first Virtual Career Fair #PKO Bank Talentów will take place in the Virtual PKO Rotunda at Decentraland. This is one of the first events of this type in the world. On that day, in our virtual space, current offers of internships and jobs at PKO Bank Polski, live presentations of bank speakers, video business cards and recruitment advice will be waiting for you. Thanks to the fair, you can learn about various areas of work in the bank - without leaving your home!

Discover the professional opportunities offered by PKO Bank Polski and meet us at the Virtual PKO Rotunda.
